\n\nA metadata  or a  accepting a  as sole argument         and returning a metadata .\n\nparam filter\n\nA  accepting a  as sole argument and returning  if         the corresponding file should be uploaded,  otherwise.\n\nreturn\n\n```\n"]}, {"name": "cdstarcat.catalog.Catalog._create", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "metadata", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "object_class", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cdstarcat.catalog.Catalog.update_metadata", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "obj", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "metadata", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "mode", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cdstarcat.catalog.Catalog.add_query", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "query", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "limit", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "offset", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cdstarcat.catalog.Catalog.add_objids", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "*objids", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kw", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["A catalog of objects in a CDSTAR instance.\n\nFor operations resulting in changes the Catalog should be used as context manager to\nmake sure changes are written to disk."]}], "exports": []}]}